import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';

function Navbar() {
  return (
    <Nav
      activeKey="/home"
      onSelect={(selectedKey) => alert(`selected ${selectedKey}`)}
    >
      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="About page">About</Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="Home page">Home</Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="Restaruant Page">Restaurants</Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="Pet Restaurant Page">Pet Restaurants</Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="Hotel Page">Hotels</Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>      
      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="Hotel Page">Recipes</Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>   
    </Nav>
  );
}

export default Navbar;
